GAL22V10
GLUE

AS       DS      HWRST  FC2    FC1     FC0    A21    A20   A19    A18      RW      GND
EXPSEL   CPUSP   HALT   RESET  IORQ    CSRAM  CSROM  DTACK BOOT   WR       PPDTACK VCC

HALT.T   =  GND
HALT.E   =  HWRST

RESET.T  =  GND
RESET.E  =  HWRST

AR       = /RESET * /HALT
BOOT.R   =  RESET *  FC2 * /FC1 *  FC0 * /A19 *  A18
         +  RESET *  FC2 * /FC1 *  FC0 *  A19 * /A18
         +  BOOT

/CPUSP   = /HWRST *  FC2 *  FC1 *  FC0 

; RAM selected
; 00 xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx and BOOT==1 (RAM is select when not in boot)
; 00 1xxx xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx and BOOT==0 (if BOOT and not 00 RAM is selected)
; 00 x1xx xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx and BOOT==0 
; 00 xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx R/W==0 and BOOT==0 (if writing and in boot RAM is selected)
/CSRAM   =  CPUSP * /AS * /DS * /A21 * /A20 *                      BOOT
         +  CPUSP * /AS * /DS * /A21 * /A20 *  A19 *              /BOOT
         +  CPUSP * /AS * /DS * /A21 * /A20 *         A18 *       /BOOT
         +  CPUSP * /AS * /DS * /A21 * /A20 *               /RW * /BOOT
; ROM selected
; 10 xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx
; 00 00xx xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx and R/W==1 (read) BOOT==0 (A read during boot at 00 will select ROM)
/CSROM   =  CPUSP * /AS * /DS *  A21 * /A20
         +  CPUSP * /AS * /DS * /A21 * /A20 * /A19 * /A18 *  RW * /BOOT

IORQ     =  /AS * A21 * A20 * A19 * A18


/PPDTACK  =  CPUSP * /CSROM
          +  CPUSP * /CSRAM
;          +  CPUSP * /EXPSEL

/WR       = RW

DTACK.T   = GND
DTACK.E   = /PPDTACK

DESCRIPTION

U1 (Address Decoder) for MECB 68008

* Onboard RAM    : $000000 - $0FFFFF (0.5MB), $080000 - $0FFFFF (0.5MB) unused (will map to expansion space in future)
* Expansion space: $100000 - $1FFFFF (1MB)
* ROM            : $200000 - $2FFFFF (0.5MB), $280000 - $2FFFFF (0.5MB) unused (will map to expansion space in future) 
* Unused         : $300000 - $3BFFFF unused (will map to expansion space in future) 
* IO             : $3C0000 - $3FFFFF (0.25 MB)
